ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ“ Trick 2: Code Ko Ek Line Me Yaad Rakho
ğŸš€ "Dictionary banao, loop chalao, end update karo, aur partition store karo!"
ğŸ’¡ Bas ye 4 cheezein yaad rakhni hain, syntax automatically fit ho jayega!

ğŸ”¥ Final Code (Syntax yaad rakhne ke liye)
python
Copy
Edit
class Solution:
    def partitionLabels(self, s):
        last_index = {ch: i for i, ch in enumerate(s)}  # Step 1: Last occurrence find karo
        
        partitions = []
        start, end = 0, 0
        
        for i, ch in enumerate(s):  # Step 2: Loop chalao
            end = max(end, last_index[ch])  # Partition expand karo
            
            if i == end:  # Step 3: Jab partition complete ho jaye
                partitions.append(end - start + 1)  # Partition ka size store karo
                start = i + 1  # Naya partition start karo
        
        return partitions
ğŸ§  Recap: 3 Key Syntax Rules
1ï¸âƒ£ Dictionary Comprehension: {ch: i for i, ch in enumerate(s)}
2ï¸âƒ£ Loop: for i, ch in enumerate(s):
3ï¸âƒ£ Condition: if i == end:

ğŸš€ Bas ye 3 cheezein yaad rakh lo, har baar syntax easily likh paoge! ğŸ˜ƒ
